data.description:
Introducing a charming tri-level gem in the heart of Centennial! Welcome to 7240 S Cherry Drive, where classic style meets modern convenience. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts an array of impressive features, including beautiful hardwood floors, an updated kitchen, and a stunning backyard oasis.

As you step inside, you'll be immediately struck by the warm and inviting ambiance of the open living spaces. The hardwood floors flow seamlessly throughout the main level, adding a touch of elegance and a durable surface that's easy to maintain.

The updated kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a stylish tile backsplash. Whether you're preparing a gourmet meal or just enjoying your morning coffee, this space is as functional as it is beautiful.

Upstairs, you'll find three spacious bedrooms, each filled with natural light and ample closet space. The two bathrooms have been tastefully updated and offer both comfort and convenience.

One of the highlights of this property is the gorgeous backyard. Step outside to a private retreat where you can entertain, relax, and enjoy the Colorado outdoors. The lush landscaping, a well-maintained lawn, and a patio area provide the perfect backdrop for summer barbecues, evening stargazing, or simply unwinding after a long day.

Located in Centennial, this home offers easy access to parks, shopping, dining, and top-rated schools. With its central location, you're never far from everything you need while still being able to enjoy the peace and quiet of a well-established neighborhood.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home. This residence combines classic charm with contemporary comforts and an outdoor paradise. Schedule your showing today and experience the best that Centennial living has to offer!
